				<font color="WHITE" font size="3px">
					<marquee style="background:Hotpink">
						The best quality dental group practice for your choice. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
						<img src="/public_html/wp-content/themes/roomchang-new/images/Logo_No_BG.png" width="25" height="23" alt="Roomchang Dental Hospital Phnom Penh Cambodia" border="0">The best dental in Phnom Penh. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
						<img src="/public_html/wp-content/themes/roomchang-new/images/Logo_No_BG.png" width="25" height="23" alt="Roomchang Dental Hospital Phnom Penh Cambodia" border="0">The best dental in Cambodia. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
						<img src="/public_html/wp-content/themes/roomchang-new/images/Logo_No_BG.png" width="25" height="23" alt="Roomchang Dental Hospital Phnom Penh Cambodia" border="0">The best dental in Town. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
						<img src="/public_html/wp-content/themes/roomchang-new/images/Logo_No_BG.png" width="25" height="23" alt="Roomchang Dental Hospital Phnom Penh Cambodia" border="0">The best dental in Cambodia. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  
						<img src="/public_html/wp-content/themes/roomchang-new/images/Logo_No_BG.png" width="25" height="23" alt="Roomchang Dental Hospital Phnom Penh Cambodia" border="0">Roomchang Dental Hospital is a renowned dental facility located in the heart of Phnom Penh.that has been providing top-quality dental services to both local and international patients since 1996.The hospital is known for its clinical strength in implant reconstruction, aesthetic dentistry, digital dentistry, children’s dentistry, orthodontics, and other specialized areas of dentistry. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
						<img src="/public_html/wp-content/themes/roomchang-new/images/Logo_No_BG.png" width="25" height="23" alt="Roomchang Dental Hospital Phnom Penh Cambodia" border="0">The hospital has a strong focus on innovation and uses the latest technology and equipment to provide patients with the best possible outcomes. The hospital’s in-house laboratory is equipped with state-of-the-art equipment, including digital scanners, CadCam technology, and 3D printers, that enable the technicians to create high-quality dental restorations with great precision and efficiency. This allows the hospital to provide patients with customized and high-quality dental restorations in a timely manner. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
						<img src="/public_html/wp-content/themes/roomchang-new/images/Logo_No_BG.png" width="25" height="23" alt="Roomchang Dental Hospital Phnom Penh Cambodia" border="0">Roomchang Dental Hospital is committed to providing high-quality dental care to all patients, regardless of their country of origin. The hospital adheres to global dental standards and guidelines, and invests in training and development programs to ensure that the team is up-to-date with the latest knowledge and skills in dentistry. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
						<img src="/public_html/wp-content/themes/roomchang-new/images/Logo_No_BG.png" width="25" height="23" alt="Roomchang Dental Hospital Phnom Penh Cambodia" border="0">The hospital’s team of dental professionals regularly attends conferences, workshops, and seminars to stay up-to-date with the latest developments in the field of dentistry. They also participate in continuing education courses and training programs offered by professional organizations and institutions. In addition to formal training and education programs, the hospital also encourages its team of dental professionals to engage in research and development activities. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
						<img src="/public_html/wp-content/themes/roomchang-new/images/Logo_No_BG.png" width="25" height="23" alt="Roomchang Dental Hospital Phnom Penh Cambodia" border="0">In addition to these initiatives, Roomchang Dental Hospital is committed to providing high-quality dental care to underserved communities in Cambodia through its charitable mission of providing free dental treatment. The hospital also supports dental healthcare education to orphanage centers and children schools around the city, educating children on the importance of maintaining good oral hygiene practices. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
						<img src="/public_html/wp-content/themes/roomchang-new/images/Logo_No_BG.png" width="25" height="23" alt="Roomchang Dental Hospital Phnom Penh Cambodia" border="0">With five branches located in different parts of Phnom Penh and a team of dentists who can communicate in various languages, including Khmer, English, Japanese, Chinese, and Malay, the hospital is easily accessible and able to cater to the needs of patients from diverse backgrounds. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
						<img src="/public_html/wp-content/themes/roomchang-new/images/Logo_No_BG.png" width="25" height="23" alt="Roomchang Dental Hospital Phnom Penh Cambodia" border="0">
					</marquee>
				</font>
				   
				
		
						


